{"tid":2346619,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"武肺啟發丨導演史提芬蘇德堡宣佈 將開拍《世紀戰疫》續集","createTime":"2020-12-30T11:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T01:19:53.000Z","uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"92a8f47717f5e591606a7c31aa60cf0784f27780","tid":2346619,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:20:42.000Z","msg":"由荷李活男星麥迪文（Matt Damon）、英國女星琦溫絲莉（Kate Winslet）、美國女星姬妮芙柏露（Gwyneth Paltrow）等於2011年主演的瘟疫電影《世紀戰疫》（Contagion），今年因為武漢肺炎病毒蔓延，帶挈該片重上熱賣流行榜。近日導演史提芬蘇德堡（Steven Soderbergh）就指，自己將會開拍此作續集。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘇德堡表示：「我正在與Scott Burns（《世紀戰疫》編劇）有新合作計劃，是《世紀戰疫》理念上的續集，但內容不一樣，你看兩齣電影會相襯，但有不用的頭髮顏色。我與Scott正在商量，下一代的《世紀戰疫》類故事會是怎樣的？我們正在努力，我們也應該加快腳步。」<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201230/IPGCG66RJFHY7EP3JTNFEMYH3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201230%2FIPGCG66RJFHY7EP3JTNFEMYH3U%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSAvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=36ccf462\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201230%2FIPGCG66RJFHY7EP3JTNFEMYH3U%2F&h=08e05487\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201230/IPGCG66RJFHY7EP3JTNFEMYH3U/</a>"},{"pid":"afa8212173bf656601935904fbb6dfacb8bbe4a4","tid":2346619,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:25:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6d10958e5e632c77dda9a2c97910c30099ee086","tid":2346619,"uid":228894,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:27:32.000Z","msg":"睇下點幫支那洗白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb09f55393f51a580c2652dee70adbb70f3671c","tid":2346619,"uid":309015,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:29:02